<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-5"><a href="#Periods_in_Chalukya_history"><span class="tocnumber">2</span> <span class="toctext">Periods in Chalukya history</span></a>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-6"><a href="#Chalukyas_of_Badami"><span class="tocnumber">2.1</span> <span class="toctext">Chalukyas of Badami</span></a></li>
