<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Chalukya_dynasty&action=edit&section=1.php.html" title="Edit section: Origins">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Origins">Origins</span></h2>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Chalukya_dynasty&action=edit&section=2.php.html" title="Edit section: Natives of Karnataka">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Natives_of_Karnataka">Natives of Karnataka</span></h3>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:172px;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:8th_century_Kannada_inscription_on_victory_pillar_at_Pattadakal.jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7f/8th_century_Kannada_inscription_on_victory_pillar_at_Pattadakal.jpg/170px-8th_century_Kannada_inscription_on_victory_pillar_at_Pattadakal.jpg" width="170" height="252" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7f/8th_century_Kannada_inscription_on_victory_pillar_at_Pattadakal.jpg/255px-8th_century_Kannada_inscription_on_victory_pillar_at_Pattadakal.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7f/8th_century_Kannada_inscription_on_victory_pillar_at_Pattadakal.jpg/340px-8th_century_Kannada_inscription_on_victory_pillar_at_Pattadakal.jpg 2x" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:8th_century_Kannada_inscription_on_victory_pillar_at_Pattadakal.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="http://bits.wikimedia.org/static-1.21wmf9/skins/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
