<li id="cite_note-occupy-63"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-occupy_63-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">This is attested to by an inscription behind the Mallikarjuna temple in Badami (Sastri 1955, p. 136)</span></li>
<li id="cite_note-decline-64"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-decline_64-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Chopra (2003), pp. 75–76, part 1</span></li>
