<li id="cite_note-kubja-88"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-kubja_88-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Pulakesi&#160;II made Vishnuvardhana the <i>Yuvaraja</i> or crown prince. Later Vishnuvardhana become the founder of the Eastern Chalukya empire (Sastri 1955, pp. 134–136, p. 312)</span></li>
